QueryScripts.Name: ImportChecking
QueryScripts.ScriptText:
$filematches = select-string "Date,Description,Amount" -path "C:\Users\tomts\Downloads\BILLS\*.csv"
$filematches | % {
   "Importing: "+$_.Path
   $content = gc $_.Path
   $tempFile = "checkingtempfile.csv"
   $content[($_.LineNumber-1)..$($content.Length)] | out-file $tempFile 
   $x = import-csv $tempFile
   del $tempFile
   $x | % { add-member -inputobject $_ -membertype noteproperty -name JSON -Value (convertto-json $_) }
   $y = $x | select json
   Write-ObjectsToSQLServer -ObjectArray $y -DestinationConnStr $env:MyDbConnStr -InputSproc [usp_Checking_Insert] -BatchSize 100
}
